## CentOS

* Temporal

```sh
loadkeys us
```

## Ubuntu

* Use to switch temporarily

```sh
sudo loadkeys dvorak
sudo loadkeys us
```
(or whatever your qwerty keymap is) to get back.


* Permamente
```sh
setxkbmap -layout us
setxkbmap -layout us -variant intl
```

